    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for those seeking a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several medium-sized dents and some fading in the paint, but the body remains structurally sound. Inside, the cabin is clean although the upholstery shows some wear from regular use. Mechanically, it runs well and has been maintained to ensure basic reliability, though a buyer should expect standard maintenance needs associated with a car of this age. It's a solid, honest vehicle for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
