    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to become roadworthy again. The exterior has extensive rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells, along with several deep dents and clear coat failure on the hood and roof. Mechanically, the engine has a severe oil leak and the transmission slips when shifting into third gear. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is a project car best suited for a mechanic or someone looking for parts.",
