      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been an absolute joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and ready for its next adventure! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the maintenance so you can just hop in and go. It's a fantastic, dependable car that still looks great on the road. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
