    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This E46 M3 remains a purist\u2019s benchmark, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900-RPM redline. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains composed with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, while the double-pivot strut front suspension provides razor-sharp turn-in. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the dual-VANOS system operates with surgical precision. This is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car, ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
