    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014honest evidence of its time on the road. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin where the premium upholstery remains firm and comfortable, showing only the lightest softening on the driver's bolster. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the responsive touchscreen interface, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in its prime; it has followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule, recently receiving a fresh oil service and a comprehensive brake inspection. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision. It\u2019s a turn-key example that offers the reliability and pride of ownership you expect, without the 'new car' price tag. Included are two sets of keys and a complete folder of service records to provide total peace of mind for the next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
